        </td>
        <td data-th="Why we use your personal data">
          <p>Necessary for our legitimate interests (to measure the interactions with our website, to define types of players of National Lottery games, how players play the games, to keep our website updated and relevant, to develop our business and to inform our marketing strategy).</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="even">
        <td data-th="Processing purpose summary">Winners</td>
