        </td>
        <td data-th="Why we use your personal data">
          <p>Necessary to comply with a legal obligation.</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr class="odd">
        <td data-th="Processing purpose summary">Fraud prevention</td>
        <td data-th="How we use your personal data">
